### Example 05 — multi-source fan-in (DEV + PROD → one table)

### DEV source
GET http://localhost:4455/odata/v4/logistics/Shipments?$top=5

### PROD source — different seed data (see _providers/logistics-service/srv/logistics-service.js)
GET http://localhost:4465/odata/v4/logistics/Shipments?$top=5

### Consolidated local target (possibly empty)
GET http://localhost:4105/odata/v4/example/Shipments?$top=5

### Both pipelines registered, each with its own origin on the tracker
GET http://localhost:4105/pipeline/Pipelines?$filter=startswith(name,'Shipments_')&$select=name,origin,mode,status
